{"title":"中国，等待夏季","authors":["蓝轲"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，等待夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京师范大学  蓝轲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光作证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界作证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们播下饱满的种籽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下民族的追求"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理想和宏伟的信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，等待夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初生的禾苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以从未有的主和弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写崭新的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使风雪在天空下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扼杀土地和碧绿的主题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寂寞的根却鸣唱不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，等待夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自东方河中升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族信念的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破坚冰的断裂层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映照执著的田塍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我们播在大地上的思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，等待夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光临播种者脚下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握金光灿灿的镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野中挥汗如雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获一场丰盈的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大地上写下中国的世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，等待夏季"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}